rtl-sdr
turns your Realtek RTL2832 based DVB dongle into a SDR receiver
======================================================================

For more information see:
http://sdr.osmocom.org/trac/wiki/rtl-sdr

This version is intended for use with sensorgnomes (https://sensorgnome.org)
and the motus wildlife tracking system (https://motus.org)

Planned Changes

- stable device selection via USB BUS:DEV selectors
  (stable against plugging / unplugging of other rtlsdr dongles)

- option to use a unix domain socket with rtl_tcp
